OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry, with some early sunshine,
OL,6,Fespecially in the east. Turning
OL,7,Fincreasingly cloudy through the
OL,8,Fmorning from the west, though should
OL,9,Fremain largely dry. Some bright or
OL,10,Fsunny intervals developing late in the
OL,11,Fafternoon. Light winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA largely cloudy but bright
OL,14,Fevening, with isolated sunny
OL,15,Fintervals. Cloud will then build from
OL,16,Fthe west overnight, with a chance of
OL,17,Foutbreaks of light rain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
