OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FCloudy to start on Tuesday,
OL,6,Fbut largely dry through much of the
OL,7,Fmorning. Spells of rain, occasionally
OL,8,Fheavy with a risk of thunder, move
OL,9,Feast in the afternoon. Light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA
OL,12,Fcloudy start with some light rain or
OL,13,Fshowers Wednesday, then brighter
OL,14,Flater. Breezy but bright start
OL,15,FThursday, chance of showers later.
OL,16,FDry, bright and warm Friday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
